 514: **ГҗВЁГҗВ°ГҗВі 2.1** ГўвӮ¬вҖқ ГҗЕҫГҗВұГҗВҪГҗВҫГҗВІГҗВёГ‘вҖҡГ‘Е’ `statusBuckets` (Г‘ВҒГ‘вҖҡГ‘вӮ¬ГҗВҫГҗВәГҗВё 456-467) ГҗВҙГҗВҫГҗВұГҗВ°ГҗВІГҗВ»ГҗВөГҗВҪГҗВёГҗВөГҗВј `pending_unconfirmed` ГҗВіГ‘вӮ¬Г‘Ж’ГҗВҝГҗВҝГ‘вҖ№:
 515: 
 516: **ГҗВўГҗВөГҗВәГ‘Ж’Г‘вҖ°ГҗВёГҗВ№ ГҗВәГҗВҫГҗВҙ:**
 517: ```jsx
 518: const statusBuckets = React.useMemo(() => {
 519:   const groups = { served: [], in_progress: [] };
 520:   todayMyOrders.forEach(o => {
 521:     const stageInfo = getOrderStatus(o);
 522:     const isServed = stageInfo?.internal_code === 'finish'
 523:       || (!stageInfo?.internal_code && ['served', 'completed'].includes((o.status || '').toLowerCase()));
 524:     const isCancelled = !stageInfo?.internal_code && (o.status || '').toLowerCase() === 'cancelled';
 525:     if (isServed) groups.served.push(o);
 526:     else if (!isCancelled) groups.in_progress.push(o);
 527:   });
 528:   return groups;
 529: }, [todayMyOrders, getOrderStatus]);
 530: ```
